{"tid":1170371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"售2000萬美元華製山寨軍服予美軍　商人被控欺詐","createTime":"2019-05-25T03:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T03:10:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c90982add27eda24a053ec7277982694a732e2e6","tid":1170371,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190524/photo/bkn-20190524161501997-0524_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190524161839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190524161501997-0524_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190524161839&h=8742b943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山寨版軍服被揭名不副實。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約一名批發商，涉嫌向美軍及供應政府物料公司，出售總值逾2000萬美元（約1.56億港元）的中國山寨軍用產品，周二（21日）被控合謀製造並向美軍出售偽造的軍裝等罪名，面臨監禁5至10年。<br />\n<br />\n羅德島地方法院指，49歲男子科恩巴什（Ramin Kohanbash）從美軍手中購買了一批軍服，再找中國的成衣商仿製。山寨軍服貼上「美國製造」標籤後，科恩巴什將仿製品銷給其他美國國內的軍服供應商，批發商則把假貨當作美製產品，售給軍方和政府。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，科恩巴什向駐紮阿富汗的美軍人員提供約200件軍事大衣中，均欠缺讓使用者難以被夜視鏡等設備偵測到的近紅外線（NIR）技術。此外，山寨軍用產品也對其安全效能作虛假陳述。例如軍事執法人員的兜帽，根本不具備阻燃功能。科恩巴什被控「販賣假冒商品」和「電匯欺詐」等罪名，案件7月12日開審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190524/mobile/bkn-20190524161501997-0524_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190524%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190524161501997-0524_00972_001.html&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62JmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=373792aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190524/mobile/bkn-20190524161501997-0524_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍都係用淘寶貨"},{"pid":"4350d34b820a913ec9828d5163cf7f5a9c88366a","tid":1170371,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"呃到美軍又幾勁"},{"pid":"abda8db97da803378a1d4da3ad3200b977985afd","tid":1170371,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"Kohanbash<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中東蛔"}]}